Routes:
/login
/bits
/pers



/login
.get - return login.ejs
.post - takes password/username, verifies and sets up session?

/login/create
.get - returns createAccount.ejs
.post - takes password/username creates account

/bits
.get - returns bits.ejs
.post - posts new bit returns bits.ejs

/bits/:id
.get returns individual bit reviewBit EJS
.put - updates the bit @ id with info in the body, returns reviewBit.ejs

/bits/:id/label
.put adds label to bit, returns yes/no
.delete removed label from bit

/bits/new
.get returns newBit.ejs

/bits/label
.post adds label to list of labels
.delete removes label from list of labels

/bits/search/:id
.get - returns results as JSON array (title, link to bit)


/pers
.get - returns pers.ejs

/pers/:id
.get - returns reviewPers.ejs
.put - updates performance @ id with data in body, returns reviewPer.EJS

/pers/new
.get returns newPer.EJS
.post - posts data in the body as new performance, returns reviewPer.ejs
